                                    Shortcuts
                                    ~~~~~~~~~
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
        F1   Shows the manual.
    control  F1   Runs the interactive help.
    control  W    Opens the SpriteLib webpage.
    control  Q    Quits SpriteLib.
    control  P    Shows the configuration window.
